msgid "`~/.config/nvim/init.vim` に以下を追記します："
msgstr "Add the following to `~/.config/nvim/init.vim`:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-29-comment-nvim-vimplug.rst:33
msgid "Neovim を起動後、以下のコマンドを実行します："
msgstr "After starting Neovim, run the following command:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-29-comment-nvim-vimplug.rst:39
msgid "これでプラグインが導入され、有効化されます。"
msgstr "The plugin is now installed and activated."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-29-comment-nvim-vimplug.rst:42
